<p><b>  Bahrain,</b><footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council.  </footnote><b> China, Cuba, Egypt,</b><footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council.  </footnote><b> India, Russian Federation, South Africa, United Arab 
